## 六、性能问题分析

### 6.1 SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE潜在问题

```java
// BinanceApiClient.java:391-409
private void cacheJsonArray(String url, String body) {
    SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.put(url, new CachedArray(body, System.currentTimeMillis()));
    if (SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.size() <= SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE_MAX_SIZE) {
        return;
    }
    // 超出容量时，逐个删除直到满足大小
    int removeCount = SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.size() - SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE_MAX_SIZE;
    Iterator<String> iterator = SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.keySet().iterator();
    while (iterator.hasNext() && removeCount > 0) {
        SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.remove(key);
        removeCount--;
    }
}
```

**问题**：
1. `size()`检查和删除操作非原子，可能短暂超出容量
2. 逐个删除效率低，高频调用时可能阻塞
3. 缓存TTL仅8秒，但删除操作遍历整个缓存

### 6.2 fetchCompleteHistoryPayload分页风险

```java
// AccountStatsPreloadManager.java:608-619
private AccountHistoryPayload fetchCompleteHistoryPayload(AccountTimeRange range) {
    AccountHistoryPayload firstPage = gatewayV2Client.fetchAccountHistory(range, "");
    List<AccountHistoryPayload> pages = new ArrayList<>();
    pages.add(firstPage);
    String nextCursor = firstPage.getNextCursor();
    while (!nextCursor.trim().isEmpty()) {
        AccountHistoryPayload nextPage = gatewayV2Client.fetchAccountHistory(range, nextCursor);
        pages.add(nextPage);
        nextCursor = nextPage.getNextCursor();  // 任何一页失败则返回不完整数据
    }
    return mergeHistoryPages(pages);
}
```

**风险**：分页中途失败会返回不完整数据，但调用方已用try-catch包裹

### 6.3 历史补拉Gate机制

```java
// AccountHistoryRefreshGate.java:16-29
public synchronized StartDecision tryStart(@Nullable String revision) {
    if (inFlight) {
        pendingRevision = safeRevision;  // 覆盖之前的pending
        return StartDecision.queued(safeRevision);
    }
    inFlight = true;
    pendingRevision = "";
    return StartDecision.started(safeRevision);
}
```

**问题**：新的revision会覆盖旧的pending revision，如果短时间内收到多个revision，只有最后一个会被处理。但这是设计选择，不是bug。

