## 二、具体问题分析

### 问题1：V2流状态变量使用volatile而非原子类（高优先级）

**文件**：`app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/service/MonitorService.java`
**行号**：101-102

```java
// 当前代码
private volatile boolean v2StreamConnected = false;
private volatile long lastV2StreamMessageAt = 0;
```

**问题**：
- `volatile`只能保证可见性，不能保证复合操作的原子性
- 当多个线程同时读写`v2StreamConnected`和`lastV2StreamMessageAt`时，可能出现竞态条件
- 例如：`if (v2StreamConnected) { lastV2StreamMessageAt = x; }`可能被中断

**风险**：状态不一致导致刷新决策错误

**修复建议**：
```java
// 方案1：使用AtomicBoolean和AtomicLong
private final AtomicBoolean v2StreamConnected = new AtomicBoolean(false);
private final AtomicLong lastV2StreamMessageAt = new AtomicLong(0);

// 方案2：封装为不可变状态对象
private final AtomicReference<V2StreamState> v2StreamState = 
    new AtomicReference<>(new V2StreamState(false, 0));

private static class V2StreamState {
    public final boolean connected;
    public final long lastMessageTime;

    public V2StreamState(boolean connected, long lastMessageTime) {
        this.connected = connected;
        this.lastMessageTime = lastMessageTime;
    }

    public V2StreamState withConnected(boolean connected) {
        return new V2StreamState(connected, this.lastMessageTime);
    }

    public V2StreamState withLastMessageTime(long time) {
        return new V2StreamState(this.connected, time);
    }
}
```

