### 问题3：SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE缓存淘汰策略低效（中优先级）

**文件**：`app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/remote/BinanceApiClient.java`
**行号**：391-409

```java
// 当前代码
public static void clearCache() {
    synchronized (SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE) {
        if (SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.size() > MAX_CACHE_SIZE) {
            // 线性遍历删除，性能差
            String firstKey = null;
            for (String key : SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.keySet()) {
                if (firstKey == null) {
                    firstKey = key;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (firstKey != null) {
                SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.remove(firstKey);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

**问题**：
- 每次只删除一个条目，清理效率低
- `MAX_CACHE_SIZE = 100`，需要多次调用才能清理
- 遍历keySet有额外开销

**风险**：在高负载时导致GC压力和延迟

**修复建议**：
```java
// 方案1：使用LinkedHashMap的LRU策略
private static final int MAX_CACHE_SIZE = 100;
private static final Map<String, CachedResponse> SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE = 
    Collections.synchronizedMap(
        new LinkedHashMap<>(16, 0.75f, true) {
            @Override
            protected boolean removeEldestEntry(Map.Entry<String, CachedResponse> eldest) {
                return size() > MAX_CACHE_SIZE;
            }
        });

// 方案2：批量清理
public static void clearCache() {
    synchronized (SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE) {
        if (SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.size() > MAX_CACHE_SIZE) {
            int toRemove = SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.size() - (MAX_CACHE_SIZE / 2);
            Iterator<String> iterator = SHARED_RESPONSE_CACHE.keySet().iterator();
            for (int i = 0; i < toRemove && iterator.hasNext(); i++) {
                iterator.next();
                iterator.remove();
            }
        }
    }
}
```

