### 问题4：fetchCompleteHistoryPayload分页失败无保护（中优先级）

**文件**：`app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/runtime/account/AccountStatsPreloadManager.java`
**行号**：608-619

```java
// 当前代码
private void fetchCompleteHistoryPayload(String symbol, long startTime, long endTime) {
    // ...
    if (accountPageFetcher.fetchWithRetry(accountId, symbol, 
        rangeStart, rangeEnd, current -> handleHistoryPage(symbol, current))) {
        accountCache.markHistoryReady(symbol, startTime, endTime);
