### 问题5：V2StreamRefreshPlanner缺少连接超时处理（中优先级）

**文件**：`app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/service/V2StreamRefreshPlanner.java`
**行号**：78-95

```java
// 当前代码
if (v2StreamConnected && currentTime - lastV2StreamMessageAt > SOCKET_STALE_TIMEOUT) {
    android.util.Log.w(TAG, "Socket连接过期，触发刷新 - " + symbol);
    if (gatewayV2StreamClient != null) {
        gatewayV2StreamClient.reconnect(symbol, lastKnownKlineId, this::onV2StreamOpened, this::onV2StreamError);
    }
}
```

**问题**：
- 重连没有指数退避，可能在网络抖动时造成频繁重连
- 没有限制最大重连次数
- 重连期间没有向用户提示状态

**风险**：网络风暴、耗电增加

**修复建议**：
```java
private int reconnectAttempts = 0;
private static final int MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS = 5;
private static final long INITIAL_BACKOFF_MS = 1000;

private void scheduleReconnect(String symbol, long lastKnownKlineId) {
    if (reconnectAttempts >= MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS) {
        android.util.Log.e(TAG, "已达到最大重连次数，放弃重连 - " + symbol);
        reconnectAttempts = 0;
        // 触发HTTP fallback
        fetchViaHttpFallback(symbol);
        return;
    }

    long backoffDelay = INITIAL_BACKOFF_MS * (1L << reconnectAttempts);
    reconnectAttempts++;

    new Handler(Looper.getMainLooper()).postDelayed(() -> {
        if (gatewayV2StreamClient != null) {
            gatewayV2StreamClient.reconnect(symbol, lastKnownKlineId, 
                () -> {
                    reconnectAttempts = 0;
                    onV2StreamOpened();
                }, 
                error -> onV2StreamError(symbol, error));
        }
    }, backoffDelay);
}
```

